The frightened children told the soldiers that they should use headlights.
According to the local pastor Yavedt Tebai, the man returned with four soldiers.
According to reports of victims and witnesses, the drunken soldiers captured the children and beat them with a hack at the rifles.
One of the soldiers shot at the children.
